SYNOPSIS
========
   int query_imp_port(void)

DESCRIPTION
===========
   Returns the port number that is used for the inter mud protocol.

HISTORY
=======
   - changed (3.2.9) -- renamed this efun to query_udp_port(). This 
     version

   is available if the driver is compiled with USE_DEPRECATED. :history 3.3 
   removed:

SEE ALSO
========
   send_udp()(E), receive_udp(M)
